comments: Murray (ATL) briefly places two hands on White (BOS) and removes them as he moves on the perimeter.
White (BOS) contests the jump shot attempt by Murray (ATL) and there is no clear and conclusive video evidence that confirms there is illegal contact.
Murray (ATL) slightly lifts his leg after the jump shot is released and marginal contact occurs with White (BOS).
Capela (ATL) retracts his arm as marginal contact occurs during Tatum's (BOS) drive.
Murray (ATL) contests Smart's (BOS) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Murray (ATL) establishes himself in White's (BOS) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Horford (BOS) places his arm against Young's (ATL) hip as he makes the pass and the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Brown (BOS) makes contact with the ball and incidental contact with Hunter's (ATL) hand on the ball to dislodge it.
Brown (BOS) gathers the ball and legally takes two steps before his passing.  His back foot slides forward after the pass is made.
White (BOS) brings his hand Young's (ATL) waist and marginal contact occurs during Young's drive.
Young (ATL) brings his off-arm towards White (BOS) and marginal contact occurs as Young releases away.
Smart (BOS) collapses his arms against his own body and incidental contact occurs with Bey (ATL) as he attempts to move around the screen.
Bey (ATL) legally contests Brown's (BOS) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
White (BOS) raises his arm to contest the dunk by Bey (ATL) and marginal contact occurs with his arm.
Brown (BOS) extends his arm forward and initiates contact with Young's (ATL) face after gathering the rebound.
Hunter (ATL) extends his arm forward and initiates contact with Tatum's (BOS) arm as he moves into his upward shooting motion.
Tatum (BOS) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
Young (ATL) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Smart's (BOS) arm.
